# Docker: Environment variables in Compose

## NginX
AP_NGINX_HTTP_PORT=80
AP_NGINX_MQTT_PORT=1883


## NATS
AP_NATS_URL=nats://nats:4222

## Grafana
AP_GRAFANA_PORT=3000

